Private Equity and Public Markets LNG is seeking third-party managers in private equity and public markets that have specialized strategies requiring proprietary expertise and relationships. In 2010, Scripps Networks rebranded RecipeZaar as [Food.com](http://www.food.com), and phased out the RecipeZaar.com brand. RecipeZaar now redirects to [Food.com](http://www.food.com). Other cooking/recipe sites include [AllRecipes](http://www.allrecipes.com), [Snacksby](http://www.snacksby.com) and [Google Recipes](http://www.google.com/base/search?a_n0=recipes&scoring=ld&a_y0=9&a_s0=0&a_r=1) (part of Google Base).
